      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HI LO RAIN (3) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.88) at this track behind King Kermaro in a Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Must come into calculations. HAPPY ETHICS (6) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Grade 5 on July 16 over 520m at Wentworth Park behind Entertainer beaten 3.5 lengths (29.98). Racing well and deserves a win. RADIANT ETHICS (7) finds it hard to break through. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (30.02) at Wentworth Park. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Expected to feature again. ZIPPING LECLERC (1) profiles nicely over this trip.",
